<i>that has accumulated from prior business</i>
<i>to present business</i>

05:14.856 --> 05:16.482
<i>to inventions.</i>

05:16.566 --> 05:19.027
<i>Any kind of creative ideas</i>
<i>he might have had.</i>

05:19.110 --> 05:20.778
<i>It's so personal to him.</i>

05:20.862 --> 05:23.656
I'm very strong-willed
