to get rid of his belongings.

05:32.582 --> 05:33.833
<i>But I'm alone now.</i>

05:34.250 --> 05:36.961
<i>I lost my husband,</i>
<i>my kids all have moved out,</i>

05:37.086 --> 05:40.381
<i>so,</i> <i>this is the perfect time for me</i>
<i>to make room for,</i>

05:40.923 --> 05:42.550
<i>you know, whatever is next.</i>

05:42.925 --> 05:46.471
<i>So, um, when Marie comes,</i>
<i>she's gonna kinda just get me started,</i>

05:46.554 --> 05:49.474
<i>but she's not gonna be here,</i>
<i>this is gonna be my full-time job,</i>

05:49.557 --> 05:50.683
<i>just cleaning my house.</i>

05:50.767 --> 05:51.601
Well, good.

05:52.143 --> 05:55.313
It's a little daunting when you see
