oh, man,
we shouldn't have got rid of, so...

06:48.825 --> 06:50.618
kinda, like, I need you to speak up

06:50.701 --> 06:53.371
and kinda be here as I go through this.

06:53.454 --> 06:55.331
- It's kind of emotional.
